d E2E suite. The container workflow at `.github/workflows/container.yml` builds and publishes the ingest image to GitHub Container Registry only after CI succeeds on `main`."},"559":{"id":"/project/verification-57","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Validate deployment artifacts locally with:"},"560":{"id":"/project/verification-58","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Run the local ingest benchmark with:"},"561":{"id":"/project/verification-59","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Package publishability is checked with:"},"562":{"id":"/project/verification-60","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#when-to-add-e2e-coverage","content":"Add E2E assertions when documentation introduces a new public workflow, API shape, query pattern, or deployment guarantee. Unit tests are enough for internal helpers, but anything shown in `/docs` should either be exercised by `npm run verify:e2e` or explicitly documented as a static/CI-only check."},"563":{"id":"/reference/api","page_id":"/reference/api","type":"page","content":"API Reference","tags":[],"url":"/reference/api"},"564":{"id":"/reference/api-0","page_id":"/reference/api","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/reference/api","content":"Rendered OpenAPI reference for the public ingest service."},"565":{"id":"/reference/api-1","page_id":"/reference/api","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/reference/api","content":"The formal API reference is generated from `openapi/clickhouse-product-analytics.openapi.yaml`."},"566":{"id":"/reference/api-2","page_id":"/reference/api","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/reference/api","content":"Endpoint pages are generated by Fumadocs OpenAPI under this section. The primary event ingestion endp